/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a moment on a highway in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a car on the road, giving a driver's eye view of the scene. The sky above is a clear blue, with the sun shining brightly, casting a warm glow over the entire scene. The highway itself is divided by a concrete barrier, providing a sense of safety and order. On either side of the road, lush green trees stand tall, their leaves rustling in the breeze. Power lines stretch out into the distance, following the path of the highway. In the far distance, the silhouettes of buildings can be seen, adding a touch of urbanity to the otherwise natural landscape. The image is a blend of man-made structures and natural elements, creating a harmonious balance.
